<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="chrome://liberator/content/help.xsl"?>

<!DOCTYPE document SYSTEM "chrome://liberator/content/liberator.dtd">

<document
    name="print"
    title="&liberator.appname; 打印"
    xmlns="http://vimperator.org/namespaces/liberator"
    xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<h1 tag="printing">打印</h1>
<toc start="2"/>

<item>
    <tags>:ha :hardcopy</tags>
    <spec>:ha<oa>rdcopy</oa><oa>!</oa></spec>
    <description>
        <p>
            Print current document. Open a GUI dialog where you can select the printer,
            number of copies, orientation, etc. When used with <oa>!</oa>, the dialog is skipped
            and the default printer used.
			打印当前文档。打开一个 GUI 对话框，你可以选择打印机，打印的份数，排版等等。如果使用 <oa>!</oa> 则跳过对话框使用默认打印机。
        </p>
    </description>
</item>


<item>
    <spec>:ha<oa>rdcopy</oa><oa>!</oa> ><a>filename</a></spec>
    <description>
        <p>同上，只不过把结果输出到 <a>filename</a>。</p>

        <note>Windows 系统上不支持。</note>
    </description>
</item>


<h2 tag="&liberator.host;-print-dialogs">&liberator.host; 打印对话框</h2>

<p>
	“打印预览”及“打印设置”对话框可以分别通过以下两个 <ex>:dialog</ex> 命令打开
</p>
<code><ex>:dialog printpreview</ex></code>
<p>
    和
</p>
<code><ex>:dialog printsetup</ex></code>
<p>
</p>

</document>
